  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Take command of a U.S. Naval fleet to wage war against an unknown alien force. Secure the seas, before it's too late.\n\nThe Wii/DS/3DS versions feature a turn based strategy gameplay approach not found in the PS3/X360 version.",
